Running the Application:

Producer Command Example:
java -jar target/kafka-manager-1.0.0-jar-with-dependencies.jar -command producer -kafkaSource 192.168.2.200:9092 -produceFilePath /tmp/messages.txt -topic my-topic -avro

Consumer Command Example:
java -jar target/kafka-manager-1.0.0-jar-with-dependencies.jar -command consumer -kafkaSource 192.168.2.200:9092 -consumeFilePath /tmp/messages.txt -topic my-topic

Copy Command Example:
java -jar target/kafka-manager-1.0.0-jar-with-dependencies.jar -command copy -kafkaSource
